OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777194388
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury's meeting
OL,4,Cwith Pope Leo will be a profound one
OL,6,FThe mere sight of her meeting the head
OL,7,Fof the Roman Catholic Church, which
OL,8,Funlike the Anglican Church still has
OL,9,Fan all-male priesthood, will be
OL,10,Fremarkable.
OL,12,FThe two, who have already called one
OL,13,Fanother "brother" and "sister", will
OL,14,Fnot only speak personally for the
OL,15,Ffirst time, but will pray together,
OL,16,Fside by side.
OL,18,FThe visit will be a profound symbol of
OL,19,Fwarmth and a shared mission for the
OL,20,Ftwo Churches, split so violently in
OL,21,Fthe Reformation under Henry VIII.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
