CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777194388
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury's meeting
OL,4,Cwith Pope Leo will be a profound one
OL,6,FBut the trip will inevitably highlight
OL,7,Ftoo, the deep division between the two
OL,8,Fon some issue - not least the
OL,9,Fordination of women. The Roman
OL,10,FCatholic Church recently ruled women
OL,11,Fcould not even be permitted to be
OL,12,Fdeacons.
OL,14,FThe Archbishop's visit marks the
OL,15,Fanniversary of a moment of history too.
OL,17,FIt's 60 years since the first meeting
OL,18,Fbetween an Archbishop of Canterbury
OL,19,Fand the Pope.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
