PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777194388
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury's meeting
OL,4,Cwith Pope Leo will be a profound one
OL,6,FThat meeting in 1966 was the first
OL,7,Ftime leaders of the Anglican and Roman
OL,8,FCatholic Churches had come together
OL,9,Fsince the Reformation in 1534, when
OL,10,FHenry VIII declared himself head of
OL,11,Fthe English Church in place of the
OL,12,FPope.
OL,14,FIt was hugely significant for Anglican-
OL,15,FRoman Catholic relations.
OL,17,FThe meeting between Pope Paul VI and
OL,18,FArchbishop Michael Ramsay took place
OL,19,Fin the Sistine Chapel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
