PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777194388
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury's meeting
OL,4,Cwith Pope Leo will be a profound one
OL,6,FA Common Declaration was issued by the
OL,7,Fpair - despite fierce opposition by
OL,8,Fmany Anglicans and Protestants -
OL,9,Fincluding Northern Ireland MP and
OL,10,Ffirebrand religious leader, Ian
OL,11,FPaisley, who saw it as an act of
OL,12,Ftreachery.
OL,14,FThe Declaration was a clear signal of
OL,15,Ftrajectory, committing the Roman
OL,16,FCatholic Church and the Anglican
OL,17,FCommunion towards unity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777194388
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury's meeting
OL,4,Cwith Pope Leo will be a profound one
OL,6,FIn a moment of deep emotion, Pope Paul
OL,7,FVI later gave Archbishop Ramsay his
OL,8,FEpiscopal ring and ever since,
OL,9,FArchbishops of Canterbury have worn
OL,10,Fthis ring whenever they visit Rome,
OL,11,Fseeing it as a symbol of the Anglican
OL,12,FCommunion's commitment to
OL,13,Freconciliation and ecumenical ties
OL,14,Fwith the Roman Catholic Church.
OL,16,FArchbishop Mullally wore the ring,
OL,17,Fmade of a large square green stone
OL,18,Fdivided by gold cross and studded with
OL,19,Ffour diamonds, at her installation
OL,20,Flast month. She will wear it again
OL,21,Ftomorrow when she meets Pope Leo.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777194388
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury's meeting
OL,4,Cwith Pope Leo will be a profound one
OL,6,FIt had to be specially re-sized to fit
OL,7,Fher finger.
OL,9,FSince that first common declaration
OL,10,Fsix decades ago, a number have been
OL,11,Fissued; all focusing on unity and
OL,12,Fshared aspects of common faith. And
OL,13,Fwhile there have been obstacles around
OL,14,FCommunion and the ordination of women
OL,15,Fwhich remain unresolved, there has
OL,16,Falways been a desire for Christian
OL,17,Funity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777194388
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury's meeting
OL,4,Cwith Pope Leo will be a profound one
OL,6,FPope Leo has, like his predecessor
OL,7,FPope Francis, indicated he is open to
OL,8,Fgiving women more senior and
OL,9,Fleadership roles within the church.
OL,10,FAnd for many progressive Roman
OL,11,FCatholics, Archbishop Sarah will be a
OL,12,Fsymbol of inspiration and hope.
OL,14,FEven though divisions remain on
OL,15,Ftheological issues, there is great
OL,16,Frespect and warmth between these two
OL,17,Fnew leaders.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
