PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777194388
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury's meeting
OL,4,Cwith Pope Leo will be a profound one
OL,6,FCatholic Cardinals attended the
OL,7,FArchbishop's installation at
OL,8,FCanterbury Cathedral last month and
OL,9,FPope Leo wrote to her personally.
OL,11,F"We know that the ecumenical journey
OL,12,Fhas not always been smooth. Despite
OL,13,Fmuch progress, our immediate
OL,14,Fpredecessors, Pope Francis and
OL,15,FArchbishop Justin Welby, acknowledged
OL,16,Ffrankly that 'new circumstances have
OL,17,Fpresented new disagreements among us'.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777194388
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury's meeting
OL,4,Cwith Pope Leo will be a profound one
OL,6,F"Nevertheless, we have continued to
OL,7,Fwalk together, because differences
OL,8,Fcannot prevent us from recognising one
OL,9,Fanother as brothers and sisters in
OL,10,FChrist."
OL,12,FThe pair have already seized an
OL,13,Fopportunity of unity in speaking out
OL,14,Fin one regard in particular: President
OL,15,FTrump.
OL,17,FThe American Pope and the American
OL,18,Fpresident have been at loggerheads in
OL,19,Frecent weeks over the war in Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
