PN,30612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777194388
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury's meeting
OL,4,Cwith Pope Leo will be a profound one
OL,6,FOn his recent tour of Africa, Pope Leo
OL,7,Fspoke of the world being "ravaged by a
OL,8,Fhandful of tyrants".
OL,10,FOn the same day, Archbishop Sarah
OL,11,Fissued a statement in solidarity with
OL,12,F"her brother Pope Leo XIV", urging
OL,13,FAnglicans to "join with his Holiness
OL,14,Fin raising our voices for peace and
OL,15,Fjustice throughout the world".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777194388
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury's meeting
OL,4,Cwith Pope Leo will be a profound one
OL,6,FSo for the first time tomorrow, after
OL,7,Fall the warm missives between them,
OL,8,Fthey will meet face to face. These
OL,9,Fpersonal moments are profoundly
OL,10,Fsignificant in forming the basis of a
OL,11,Ffriendship and collaboration.
OL,13,FThe Archbishop of Canterbury will
OL,14,Ffirst have a private audience with the
OL,15,FPope in the morning. She will then
OL,16,Fjoin him for midday prayer in the
OL,17,FChapel of Urban VIII within the
OL,18,FApostolic Palace, accompanied by the
OL,19,Falso new Roman Catholic Archbishop of
OL,20,FWestminster, Richard Moth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777194388
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury's meeting
OL,4,Cwith Pope Leo will be a profound one
OL,6,FIn anticipation Archbishop Sarah has
OL,7,Fsaid: "I give thanks for the deepening
OL,8,Fdialogue and fellowship between
OL,9,FAnglicans and Catholics over the last
OL,10,Fsixty years. It is a joy and privilege
OL,11,Fto meet and pray with His Holiness
OL,12,FPope Leo XIV and I look forward to our
OL,13,Fconversation and prayer."
OL,15,FOf course, English is their native
OL,16,Flanguage which will make talking to
OL,17,Feach other much easier without the
OL,18,Fneed for interpreters.
OL,20,FThere are so many questions ahead of
OL,21,Fthis historic meeting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777194388
OL,3,CArchbishop of Canterbury's meeting
OL,4,Cwith Pope Leo will be a profound one
OL,6,FWhat will they discuss? Will they get
OL,7,Fon? How will Leo respond to a female
OL,8,Fleader of the Anglican Communion? What
OL,9,Fpath for Christian unity do they
OL,10,Fforesee?
OL,12,FWill the pair use this first personal
OL,13,Fmeeting to issue another statement
OL,14,Fabout the direction in which President
OL,15,FTrump appears to be taking the world?
OL,17,FHow might the current vivid spotlight
OL,18,Fon Pope Leo - who has found his voice
OL,19,Fso powerfully - serve both leaders to
OL,20,Famplify a message of peace?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
